# ORIG TITLE    Ocalan to make an “historic appeal” from prison . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Jailed Kurdish separatist leader Abdullah Ocalan is to make what’s described as an “historic” appeal from his Turkish prison this Thursday. It has raised expectations of a ceasefire in a 28-year-old conflict that has killed an estimated 40,000 people. There has been no comment from the Turkish government. 
